\c 17
\s Ukunqotshwa kweSamariya lokuchithwa kwelakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lambili kaAhazi inkosi yakoJuda uHosheya indodana kaEla waba yinkosi eSamariya phezu kukaIsrayeli; \add wabusa\add* iminyaka eyisificamunwemunye.
\v 2 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, loba kunjalo kungenjengamakhosi akoIsrayeli ayengaphambi kwakhe.
\v 3 UShalimaneseri inkosi yeAsiriya wenyuka wamelana laye; uHosheya wasesiba yinceku yakhe, wathela umthelo kuye.
\v 4 Kodwa inkosi yeAsiriya yafica ugobe kuHosheya, ngoba wayethume izithunywa kuSo inkosi yeGibhithe, ka\add za\add*be esenyusa umthelo enkosini yeAsiriya umnyaka ngomnyaka. Ngakho inkosi yeAsiriya yamvalela yambopha entolongweni.
\v 5 Inkosi yeAsiriya yasisenyukela kulo lonke ilizwe, yenyukela eSamariya, yayivimbezela iminyaka emithathu.
\v 6 Ngomnyaka wesificamunwemunye kaHosheya, inkosi yeAsiriya yathumba iSamariya yathumbela uIsrayeli eAsiriya, yabahlalisa eHala leHabori, umfula weGozani, lemizini yamaMede.
\p
\v 7 Lokhu-ke kwenzeka ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli babonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wabo eyayibenyuse elizweni leGibhithe ibasusa ngaphansi kwesandla sikaFaro inkosi yeGibhithe, babesabe abanye onkulunkulu,
\v 8 bahamba ezimisweni zezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayizixotshe elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, lezamakhosi akoIsrayeli, ayezenzile.
\v 9 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli benza ensitha izinto ezingalunganga bemelene leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo. Babezakhele indawo eziphakemeyo kuyo yonke imizi yabo, kusukela enqabeni yabalindi kuze kube semzini obiyelweyo.
\v 10 Basebezimisela insika eziyizithombe lezixuku phezu kwawo wonke amaqaqa aphakemeyo langaphansi kwaso sonke isihlahla esiluhlaza.
\v 11 Basebetshisa lapho impepha endaweni zonke eziphakemeyo, njengezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazikhokhelela ekuthunjweni phambi kwabo; benza izinto ezimbi ukuyithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 12 Ngoba bakhonza izithombe, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayithe ngazo kubo: Kaliyikuyenza linto.
\v 13 Kanti iN\nd kosi\nd* yafakaza imelene loIsrayeli njalo imelene loJuda ngesandla sabo bonke abaprofethi \add l\add*ababoni bonke isithi: Phendukani endleleni zenu ezimbi, ligcine imithetho yami, izimiso zami, njengokomlayo wonke engawulaya oyihlo lengawuthumela kini ngesandla senceku zami abaprofethi.
\v 14 Loba kunjalo kabalalelanga, kodwa benza lukhuni intamo yabo, njengentamo yaboyise, abangakholwanga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wabo.
\v 15 Njalo bala izimiso zayo lesivumelwano sayo eyasenza laboyise lezifakazelo zayo eyazifakaza imelene labo, balandela ize, baba yize, balandela izizwe ezazibahanqile, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayibalaye ngazo ukuthi bangenzi njengazo.
\v 16 Bayitshiya yonke imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo, bazenzela izithombe ezibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa, amathole amabili, benza isixuku, bakhothamela lonke ibutho lamazulu, bakhonza uBhali.
\v 17 Benza amadodana abo lamadodakazi abo adabule emlilweni, benza ukuvumisa, benza imilingo, bazithengisela ukwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* ukuyithukuthelisa.
\v 18 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yamthukuthelela kakhulu uIsrayeli, yabasusa ebusweni bayo; kakusalanga loyedwa ngaphandle kwesizwe sakoJuda kuphela.
\v 19 Laye uJuda kayigcinanga imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo, kodwa bahamba ngezimiso zikaIsrayeli abazenzayo.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiyala yonke inzalo yakoIsrayeli, yayihlupha, yayinikela esandleni sabaphangi, yaze yabalahla yabasusa phambi kwayo.
\v 21 Ngoba yamdabula uIsrayeli imsusa endlini kaDavida, basebebeka uJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati ukuthi abe yinkosi. UJerobhowamu wamqhuba wamphambula uIsrayeli ekulandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, wabenza bona isono esikhulu.
\v 22 Ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahamba ngazo zonke izono zikaJerobhowamu azenzayo, kabasukanga kuzo,
\v 23 iN\nd kosi\nd* yaze yamsusa uIsrayeli phambi kwayo njengokutsho kwayo ngesandla sazo zonke inceku zayo abaprofethi\x + 17.13. 1 Kho. 9.7.\x*. Ngakho uIsrayeli wathunjwa wasuswa elizweni lakhe wasiwa eAsiriya kuze kube lamuhla\x + 17.6.\x*.
\s Abantu bezizweni bahlaliswa eSamariya
\p
\v 24 Inkosi yeAsiriya yasiletha \add abantu\x + Ezra 4.2,9,10.\x*\add* abavela eBhabhiloni\x + 17.30. Gen. 10.10.\x* labavela eKutha labavela eAva labavela eHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x* labavela eSefavayimi\x + 17.31. 18.34. 19.13.\x*, yabahlalisa emizini yeSamariya esikhundleni sabantwana bakoIsrayeli, badla ilifa leSamariya, bahlala emizini yayo.
\v 25 Kwasekusithi ekuqaleni kokuhlala kwabo khona kabayesabanga iN\nd kosi\nd*; ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yathumela izilwane phakathi kwabo ezabulala \add abanye\add* babo.
\v 26 Ngakho bakhuluma enkosini yeAsiriya besithi: Izizwe owazisusayo wazihlalisa emizini yeSamariya kaziwazi umkhuba kaNkulunkulu walelolizwe; ngakho uthumele izilwane phakathi kwazo, khangela-ke ziyazibulala, ngoba kaziwazi umkhuba kaNkulunkulu walelolizwe.
\v 27 Inkosi yeAsiriya yasilaya isithi: Yisani khona omunye wabapristi elabathumbayo besuka lapho; kabayehlala khona, kabafundise umkhuba kaNkulunkulu walelolizwe.
\v 28 Ngakho omunye wabapristi ababebathumbe besuka eSamariya weza wahlala eBhetheli\x + 1 Kho. 12.29.\x*, wabafundisa ukuthi bangayesaba njani iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 29 Loba kunjalo zonke izizwe zenza onkulunkulu bazo, zabafaka ezindlini zezindawo eziphakemeyo amaSamariya azenzayo, yileso laleso isizwe emizini yazo ezihlala kuyo.
\v 30 Labantu beBhabhiloni benza uSukothi-Benothi, labantu beKuthi benza uNerigali, labantu beHamathi benza uAshima,
\v 31 lamaAvi enza uNibazi loTaritaki, lamaSefavayimi ayetshisa abantwana bawo emlilweni esenzela uAdrameleki loAnameleki onkulunkulu beSefavayimi.
\v 32 Babeyesaba leN\nd kosi\nd*, bazenzela abapristi bezindawo eziphakemeyo kwabaphansi kakhulu babo, ababebasebenzela ezindlini zezindawo eziphakemeyo.
\v 33 Babeyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo babekhonza onkulunkulu babo njengomkhuba wezizwe ezabathumbayo besuka lapho.
\v 34 Kuze kube lamuhla benza njengemikhuba yakuqala. Kabayesabi iN\nd kosi\nd*, kabenzi njengezimiso zabo lanjengezimiselo zabo lanjengomlayo lanjengomthetho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakulaya abantwana bakaJakobe, owamutha ibizo elithi uIsrayeli.
\v 35 IN\nd kosi\nd* eyenza isivumelwano labo, yabalaya isithi: Kaliyikwesaba abanye onkulunkulu, lingabakhothameli, lingabasebenzeli, lingabahlabeli.
\v 36 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalenyusa elizweni leGibhithe ngamandla amakhulu langengalo eyeluliweyo, yona lizayesaba njalo yona lizayikhothamela njalo yona lizayihlabela.
\v 37 Lezimiso lezimiselo lomlayo lomthetho eyalibhalela khona, lizaqaphelisa ukukwenza zonke izinsuku, lingesabi abanye onkulunkulu.
\v 38 Lesivumelwano engasenza lani lingasikhohlwa, lingesabi abanye onkulunkulu.
\v 39 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu lizayesaba; yona-ke izalikhulula esandleni sezitha zenu zonke.
\v 40 Loba kunjalo kabalalelanga, kodwa benza njengomkhuba wabo wakuqala.
\v 41 Lezizizwe zayesaba-ke iN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa zakhonza izithombe zazo ezibaziweyo; bobabili abantwana bazo labantwana babantwana bazo, njengokwenza kwaboyise benza \add la\add*bo kuze kube lamuhla\x + 17.32,33.\x*.